                    h5#charge_serveurModalLabel.modal-title The server load
                    button.btn-close(type='button' data-bs-dismiss='modal' aria-label='Close')
                .modal-body
                    p A website can be brought to make requests to other websites to get new features, plugins, ... It goes without saying that these requests consume, the server load indicates the number of requests made by a website. The more a site has a high server load, the more it will consume.

